This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function apply_filter_flag (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['mms4_dis_dist_brst', 'mms4_dis_steptable_parity_brst']. Note that some COMPONENTS may not be available from the HAPI interface. They are accessible from the raw CDF files, however.
